On Thursday, dozens of houses of the October and Railway regions of Krasnoyarsk will be left without cold water

06 Nov 2019, 07:42

The press secretary of KrasKom, Tatyana Lukina, said that tomorrow, November 7, there will be no cold water in parts of the Oktyabrsky and Zheleznodorozhny district houses.
Turn off the water from 9 to 19 hours in order to embed a new valve and a section of the pipeline into the water supply system. There will be no water at the following addresses:

L. Ketskhoveli, 17A, 65A, 67k.1, 67k.2;
Pushkin, 9, 11, 22a, 28, 32;
Sopochnaya, 36,, 36A
